06/09/2022 07:52:18 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: a waste of money [SEP] content: I bought this product due to the sloping seats in my Dodge Caravan and thought that it was going to be very useful. (the carseat should not move more than 1 inch in any direction) I again tried to use the leveler when we converted to a convertible carseat,and yet again no luck. I recommend the poll noddles, they are much easier to use and a fraction of the cost.

We used it for a while, but it was very hard (not to mention unpleasent) to push the diapers down. It really took some force. The bag constantly ripped. I always had to seperately bag messy diapers because when they got pushed down, some always "escaped". I finally got so annoyed with it I didn't use it any more. Save your money, go with the Neat instead!

There was no way to get a tight fit for the carseat using the 1 inch rule. (the carseat should not move more than 1 inch in any direction) I again tried to use the leveler when we converted to a convertible carseat,and yet again no luck. I recommend the poll noddles, they are much easier to use and a fraction of the cost.

06/09/2022 08:26:22 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: Incomplete and poorly organized [SEP] content: I am currently taking a classroom course to get the MCSE, and the Global Knowledge Certification Press MCSE study guides are the books provided by the school. We have two certs left to go, but my class has already convinced the administration to drop these books. Yes, they are that bad. Explanations that assume you already understand the topic, or worse yet assume the topic is self-explanatory are the norm in these books. Labs leave out critical steps that make doing any part of the exercise impossible. All in all, this entire series of MCSE books is not worth your hard earned money. If you are seriously studying for your MCSE, stay as far away from this series as you can.

06/09/2022 08:43:50 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: Incomplete and poorly organized [SEP] content: I am currently taking a classroom course to get the MCSE, and the Global Knowledge Certification Press MCSE study guides are the books provided by the school. We have two certs left to go, but my class has already convinced the administration to drop these books. Yes, they are that bad. Explanations that assume you already understand the topic, or worse yet assume the topic is self-explanatory are the norm in these books. Labs leave out critical steps that make doing any part of the exercise impossible. All in all, this entire series of MCSE books is not worth your hard earned money. If you are seriously studying for your MCSE, stay as far away from this series as you can.

06/11/2022 16:36:25 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: a waste of money [SEP] content: I bought this product due to the sloping seats in my Dodge Caravan and thought that it was going to be very useful. I recommend the poll noddles, they are much easier to use and a fraction of the cost.

It was always Tom's portrayal of the battle or espionage, and the realpolitik which motivates governments and the military alike, which captured my imagination.I can't maintain interest in a thousand page book if it reads like a soap opera!

06/11/2022 17:11:03 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: Incomplete and poorly organized [SEP] content: I am currently taking a classroom course to get the MCSE, and the Global Knowledge Certification Press MCSE study guides are the books provided by the school. We have two certs left to go, but my class has already convinced the administration to drop these books. Yes, they are that bad. Explanations that assume you already understand the topic, or worse yet assume the topic is self-explanatory are the norm in these books. Labs leave out critical steps that make doing any part of the exercise impossible. All in all, this entire series of MCSE books is not worth your hard earned money. If you are seriously studying for your MCSE, stay as far away from this series as you can.

06/11/2022 17:28:06 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: Incomplete and poorly organized [SEP] content: I am currently taking a classroom course to get the MCSE, and the Global Knowledge Certification Press MCSE study guides are the books provided by the school. We have two certs left to go, but my class has already convinced the administration to drop these books. Yes, they are that bad. Explanations that assume you already understand the topic, or worse yet assume the topic is self-explanatory are the norm in these books. Labs leave out critical steps that make doing any part of the exercise impossible. All in all, this entire series of MCSE books is not worth your hard earned money. If you are seriously studying for your MCSE, stay as far away from this series as you can.

06/11/2022 17:45:22 - INFO - __main__ -  [amazon_polarity] title: Incomplete and poorly organized [SEP] content: I am currently taking a classroom course to get the MCSE, and the Global Knowledge Certification Press MCSE study guides are the books provided by the school. Labs leave out critical steps that make doing any part of the exercise impossible. All in all, this entire series of MCSE books is not worth your hard earned money. Labs leave out critical steps that make doing any part of the exercise impossible. All in all, this entire series of MCSE books is not worth your hard earned money. If you are seriously studying for your MCSE, stay as far away from this series as you can.
